      "id": "software_engineering-natural-language-processing",
      "name": "Code Refactoring Workflow",
      "description": "Refactoring improves internal design without changing behavior: after spotting a code smell, test coverage is ensured (adding characterization tests if needed), then small behavior-preserving transformations are applied and verified by tests; any failure is reverted, and the cycle repeats until no smells remain.",
